org.bubblecloud.zigbee.api.cluster.impl.general.alarms

Class AlarmsClusterFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bubblecloud.zigbee.api.cluster.impl.general.alarms.AlarmsClusterFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClusterFilter

    public class AlarmsClusterFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClusterFilter
    This class should filter out all the ZigBee cluster that do not belong to the
    AlarmResponse type from the Alarms cluster, by checking the data itself.

    NOTE:to use this class the FILTER constant should be used
